description:
With this client library you can easily add electronic signatures to your systems and exisitng work-flows based on the Underskrift API. 

You can add electronic signatures to web forms, documents or other data regardless of file type. If you have security classed documents or if all parties have access to the documents you don't need to send the documents to us, you just have to send the documents SHA2-512 hash.

A case can be signed by one or multiple parties. Information about the parties can either be specified upfront or collected when signing. You choose if you want to communicate with the parites or if you want to use alread made templates.

Depending on the scenario different types of identification can be used, currently electronic-id, SMS and touch signatures are supported.
summary: This library enables signing of documents through Underskrift.se's API.
title: Underskrift.Client
